channel.title: My current project + progress ( please comment )
channel.description:
hello i am working on a project, and i am using elitescape as a base
features it will have when finished
-f2p -p2p (adding my own members system) -new quests -new members area/commands -proper rs teleports ( server isnt world wide, its like f2p on rs. just the main towns ) -barrows ( real 1s underground ) -pest control -fight pits ( f2p ) -jad 63 waves -and many more
progress
-f2p 100% -p2p (adding my own members system) - 30% -new quests-10% -new members area/commands - 0% -proper rs teleports 45% ( server isnt world wide, its like f2p on rs. just the main towns ) -barrows ( real 1s underground ) - 15% //creds to delta for barrows base -pest control - 60% //creds to delta for pc base -fight pits ( f2p ) - 100% //creds to delta -jad 63 waves - 100% //creds to delta
a simple vid of what ive done so far
http://uk.youtube.com/watch?v=EfJfgCZgvTI
//ignore the client just look at what its showing you, yes i no my client is messed...im currently working on it, until its fixed i cant take screenys
- ive changed the order of the quests so members is at top, and ive added all my items i want as member items
currently working on - teles and minigames, making em p2p n f2p
